foundry-anvil (1.0.4) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Slim to thin umbrella: Depends now foundry-core + foundry-desktop.
    All tool deps moved to foundry-core; KDE deps moved to foundry-desktop.
    Existing Ubuntu users should install foundry-core instead.
    See docs/plans/2026-05-28-foundry-core-desktop-split.md.

